3834&amp;resourcekey=0-WwPflJCoeclm3TbDONCfDA&amp;rtpof=true&amp;sd=true\" target=\"_blank\" onclick=\"return HMTrackTopiclink(this);\" class=\"weblink\" title=\"Tümünü okumak için tıklayınız.\">Vergi Dairesi Müd.ne beyiye talebi için excel formatındaki aşağıdaki metnin orjinalini indirmek için tıklayınız.</a></p>\n\n<hr style=\"height:1px; color:#000000; border-width:0; background-color:#000000;\" /><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a class=\"dropdown-toggle\" href=\"javascript:HMToggle('toggle','TOGGLE0186A1')\"> BEYİYE İÇİN DİLEKÇE</a></p>\n\n<div id=\"TOGGLE0186A1\" class=\"dropdown-toggle-body\" style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 0; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;\"><table class=\"toggle\" >\n\n<tr class=\"toggle\">\n\n<td class=\"toggle\"><p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">T.C.</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">ADALET &nbsp;BAKANLIĞI</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> &nbsp; ( &nbsp; ) NOTERLİĞİ &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">( &nbsp; ) VERGİ &nbsp;DAİRESİ &nbsp;MÜDÜRLÜĞÜ ' NE</p>\n\n<p> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  492 &nbsp;Sayılı &nbsp;Harçlar &nbsp;Kanununun, &nbsp;488 &nbsp;Sayılı &nbsp;Damga &nbsp;Vergisi &nbsp;Kanunu &nbsp;ve &nbsp; 210 &nbsp;Sayılı &nbsp;Değerli Kağıtlar &nbsp;Kanunu &nbsp;hükümlerince &nbsp;tahsil &nbsp;edilen &nbsp;ve &nbsp;1512 &nbsp;Sayılı &nbsp;Noterlik &nbsp;Kanunu &nbsp;hükümlerince &nbsp;15 &nbsp;günde &nbsp;bir ( &nbsp; ) Vergi Dairesi Müdürlüğü'ne yasal &nbsp;süresi içinde yatırıldığını &nbsp;gösteren &nbsp;makbuz &nbsp;asılları ekte sunulmuş &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  olup, Beyiye &nbsp;bedellerini &nbsp;aşağıda &nbsp;belirtilen &nbsp;banka &nbsp;hesaplarına &nbsp;aktarılması &nbsp;hususunu; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  talep ederim. &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<div style=\"text-align: left; text-indent: 0; padding: 0 0 0 0; margin: 0 0 0 0;\"><table style=\"width:100%; border:none; border-spacing:0;\">\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:top; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">NOTER</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">ADI VE SOYADI-ÜNVANI</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n<tr>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n</td>\n\n<td style=\"vertical-align:middle; padding:0; border:none\"><p style=\"text-align: center;\">RESMİ MÜHÜR VE İMZA</p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n</div>\n\n<p> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </p>\n\n<p> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>TC.Kimlik No : &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Banka &nbsp;Adı &nbsp;: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;   &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Şube &nbsp; &nbsp;Adı &nbsp;: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Şube Kodu &nbsp;: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Hesap &nbsp; No &nbsp;: &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>IBAN &nbsp; &nbsp; No &nbsp;: &nbsp; </p>\n\n</td>\n\n</tr>\n\n</table>\n\n</div>\n\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"p_Normal\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <a href=\"noterlik-kanunu.html\" class=\"topiclink\">Noterlik Kanunu</a>nun yürürlüğe girdiği 5 Mayıs 1972 tarihinden bu yana, aynı yasanın 118. ve 119. maddeleri gereğince noterlerin yaptıkları işlemlere ait vergi, resim ve harçları makbuz karşılığı tahsil etmekte ve her ay iki dönem halinde düzenleyecekleri bir beyanname ile ilgili vergi dairesine yatırmakta ve tahsil ettikleri vergi, resim ve harç tutarları üzerinden % 3 oranında noter hissesi almaktadırlar. </p>\n\n<p>Bu gelirlerden harç, damga vergisi ve resimden alınması gereken % 3 oranındaki noter hissesinin tahsil edilip edilmediğine bakılmaksızın ilgili ay cetvellerinde yerlerinde gösterilmesi gerekir.</p>\n\n<p>Noterler, tahsil ettikleri harç ve vergi üzerinden % 3, değerli kağıt bedelleri üzerinden % 2 oranında noter hissesi (beyiye) alırlar. Bu hissenin ödenmesi, beyiye aidatlarının ödenmesine ilişkin hükümlere göre yapılır.  </p>\n\n<p> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;  Noterliklere damga vergisi ve harç tutarları üzerinden ödenen %3 nispetindeki noter hissesi ile değerli kağıt bedelleri üzerinden ödenen % 2 nispetindeki satış aidatı üzerinden, ödemeyi yapan saymanlıkça kesilen damga vergisi tutarlarının noterlik giderine kaydedilmesine kanuni bir engel bulunmamaktadır.</p>\n\n\n\n<!--ZOOMSTOP-->\n\n\n\n\n\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\" \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n\n\n\n<head>\n\n<meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=utf-8\" />\n\n\n\n\n\n   <script type=\"text/javascript\">\n\n     HMSyncTOC(\"index.html\", \"beyiye-icin-dilekce.html\");\n\n   </script>\n\n</head>\n\n<body>\n\n<!-- Google tag (gtag.js) -->\n\n<script async src=\"https://www.googletagmanager.com/gtag/js?id=G-L1LQTG9GMG\"></script>\n\n<script>\n\n  window.dataLayer = window.dataLayer || [];\n\n  function gtag(){dataLayer.push(arguments);}\n\n  gtag('js', new Date());\n\n\n\n  gtag('config', 'G-L1LQTG9GMG');\n\n</script>\n\n\n\n<hr>\n\n<div class=\"topicfooter\"><p class=\"topicfooter\"> <a href=\"hangi-konular-guncellendi.html\" target=\"hmcontent\">Güncelleme: 01.12.2022</a></p>\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"topicfooter\">\n\n<p class=\"topicfooter\"> <a href=\"fihrist.html\" targ